kpi_definitions.name: source_fdn
kpi_definitions.expression: cell_guid.fdn FROM kpi://relation_guid_source_guid_target_guid LEFT JOIN kpi://cell_guid ON relation_guid_source_guid_target_guid.source_cell_cgi_daily = cell_guid.cgi

kpi_definitions.name: contiguity
kpi_definitions.expression: 100 * (SUM(relation_guid_source_guid_target_guid.out_succ_ho_intraf)) / (SUM(relation_guid_source_guid_target_guid.out_succ_ho_intraf) + SUM(relation_guid_source_guid_target_guid.out_succ_ho_interf)) FROM kpi_post_agg://relation_guid_source_guid_target_guid WHERE relation_guid_source_guid_target_guid.intra_site = false OR relation_guid_source_guid_target_guid.intra_site IS NULL

kpi_definitions.name: cell_availability
kpi_definitions.expression: 100 * (96 * 900 - FIRST( kpi_cell_guid_1440.pm_cell_downtime_auto_daily, true ) - FIRST( kpi_cell_guid_1440.pm_cell_downtime_man_daily, true )) / (96 * 900) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_1440

kpi_definitions.name: coverage_balance_distance_bin
kpi_definitions.expression: PERCENTILE_INDEX_90(kpi_cell_guid_1440.num_samples_ta) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_1440 inner join cm://cell_sector on kpi_cell_guid_1440.oss_id = cell_sector.cell_oss_id AND kpi_cell_guid_1440.fdn = cell_sector.cell_fdn

kpi_definitions.name: coverage_balance_distance
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST( CALCULATE_PERCENTILE_DISTANCE(kpi_cell_guid_1440.num_samples_ta, 90), true ) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_1440 inner join cm://cell_sector on kpi_cell_guid_1440.oss_id = cell_sector.cell_oss_id AND kpi_cell_guid_1440.fdn = cell_sector.cell_fdn

kpi_definitions.name: coverage_balance_signal_index
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(CALCULATE_PERCENTILE_BIN(kpi_cell_guid_1440.num_samples_ta, 80), true) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_1440 inner join cm://cell_sector on kpi_cell_guid_1440.oss_id = cell_sector.cell_oss_id AND kpi_cell_guid_1440.fdn = cell_sector.cell_fdn

kpi_definitions.name: reference_cell_sector_fdn
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST( kpi_cell_sector_1440.cell_fdn, true ) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_sector_1440 inner join kpi://sector on kpi_cell_sector_1440.sector_id = sector.sector_id AND kpi_cell_sector_1440.coverage_balance_distance = sector.max_coverage_balance_distance

kpi_definitions.name: reference_cell
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST( kpi_sector.reference_cell_sector_fdn, true ) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_sector_1440 inner join kpi_db://kpi_sector on kpi_cell_sector_1440.sector_id = kpi_sector.sector_id

kpi_definitions.name: coverage_balance_distance_reference_bin
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST( estimated_cells.coverage_balance_distance_bin, true ) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_sector_1440 left join kpi_db://kpi_cell_sector_1440 AS estimated_cells where kpi_cell_sector_1440.reference_cell = estimated_cells.cell_fdn

kpi_definitions.name: coverage_balance_distance_reference
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST( estimated_cells.coverage_balance_distance, true ) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_sector_1440 left join kpi_db://kpi_cell_sector_1440 AS estimated_cells where kpi_cell_sector_1440.reference_cell = estimated_cells.cell_fdn

kpi_definitions.name: coverage_balance_signal_reference_index
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(estimated_cells.coverage_balance_signal_index, true) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_sector_1440 left join kpi_db://kpi_cell_sector_1440 AS estimated_cells where kpi_cell_sector_1440.reference_cell = estimated_cells.cell_fdn

kpi_definitions.name: coverage_balance_ratio_distance
kpi_definitions.expression: 100 * FIRST( kpi_cell_sector_1440.coverage_balance_distance, true ) / FIRST( kpi_cell_sector_1440.coverage_balance_distance_reference, true ) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_sector_1440

kpi_definitions.name: coverage_balance_signal_range_upper_index
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(greatest(kpi_cell_sector_1440.coverage_balance_signal_index, kpi_cell_sector_1440.coverage_balance_signal_reference_index), true) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_sector_1440 LEFT JOIN kpi_db://kpi_cell_sector ON kpi_cell_sector_1440.cell_oss_id = kpi_cell_sector.cell_oss_id AND kpi_cell_sector_1440.cell_fdn = kpi_cell_sector.cell_fdn AND kpi_cell_sector_1440.sector_id = kpi_cell_sector.sector_id WHERE kpi_cell_sector.coverage_balance_signal_range_calculation_time < TO_TIMESTAMP(''${param.recalculation_date}'') OR kpi_cell_sector.coverage_balance_signal_range_calculation_time IS NULL ${param.sectors_for_signal_range_recalculation}

kpi_definitions.name: coverage_balance_signal_range_lower_index
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(least(kpi_cell_sector_1440.coverage_balance_signal_index, kpi_cell_sector_1440.coverage_balance_signal_reference_index), true) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_sector_1440 LEFT JOIN kpi_db://kpi_cell_sector ON kpi_cell_sector_1440.cell_fdn = kpi_cell_sector.cell_fdn AND kpi_cell_sector_1440.cell_oss_id = kpi_cell_sector.cell_oss_id AND kpi_cell_sector_1440.sector_id = kpi_cell_sector.sector_id WHERE kpi_cell_sector.coverage_balance_signal_range_calculation_time < TO_TIMESTAMP(''${param.recalculation_date}'') OR kpi_cell_sector.coverage_balance_signal_range_calculation_time IS NULL ${param.sectors_for_signal_range_recalculation}

kpi_definitions.name: coverage_balance_signal_range_calculation_time
kpi_definitions.expression: TO_TIMESTAMP(''${param.current_date}'') FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_sector_1440 LEFT JOIN kpi_db://kpi_cell_sector ON kpi_cell_sector_1440.cell_fdn = kpi_cell_sector.cell_fdn AND kpi_cell_sector_1440.cell_oss_id = kpi_cell_sector.cell_oss_id AND kpi_cell_sector_1440.sector_id = kpi_cell_sector.sector_id WHERE kpi_cell_sector.coverage_balance_signal_range_calculation_time < TO_TIMESTAMP(''${param.recalculation_date}'') OR kpi_cell_sector.coverage_balance_signal_range_calculation_time IS NULL ${param.sectors_for_signal_range_recalculation}

kpi_definitions.name: num_samples_rsrp_ta_candidate
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST( kpi_cell_guid_1440.num_samples_rsrp_ta, true ) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_sector_1440 inner join kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_1440 on kpi_cell_sector_1440.cell_oss_id = kpi_cell_guid_1440.oss_id AND kpi_cell_sector_1440.cell_fdn = kpi_cell_guid_1440.fdn

kpi_definitions.name: num_samples_rsrp_ta_reference
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST( kpi_cell_guid_1440.num_samples_rsrp_ta, true ) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_sector_1440 inner join kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_1440 on kpi_cell_sector_1440.reference_cell = kpi_cell_guid_1440.fdn AND kpi_cell_sector_1440.cell_oss_id = kpi_cell_guid_1440.oss_id

kpi_definitions.name: num_samples_rsrp_candidate
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(SUM_ARRAY_SLICE(cell_sector.num_samples_rsrp_ta_candidate, kpi_cell_sector.coverage_balance_signal_range_lower_index, kpi_cell_sector.coverage_balance_signal_range_upper_index), true) FROM kpi://cell_sector inner join kpi_db://kpi_cell_sector on cell_sector.cell_fdn = kpi_cell_sector.cell_fdn AND cell_sector.cell_oss_id = kpi_cell_sector.cell_oss_id AND cell_sector.sector_id = kpi_cell_sector.sector_id

kpi_definitions.name: num_samples_rsrp_reference
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(SUM_ARRAY_SLICE(cell_sector.num_samples_rsrp_ta_reference, kpi_cell_sector.coverage_balance_signal_range_lower_index, kpi_cell_sector.coverage_balance_signal_range_upper_index), true) FROM kpi://cell_sector inner join kpi_db://kpi_cell_sector on cell_sector.cell_fdn = kpi_cell_sector.cell_fdn AND cell_sector.cell_oss_id = kpi_cell_sector.cell_oss_id AND cell_sector.sector_id = kpi_cell_sector.sector_id

kpi_definitions.name: num_samples_bad_rsrp_ta_candidate
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST( kpi_cell_guid_1440.num_samples_bad_rsrp_ta, true ) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_sector_1440 inner join kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_1440 on kpi_cell_sector_1440.cell_fdn = kpi_cell_guid_1440.fdn AND kpi_cell_sector_1440.cell_oss_id = kpi_cell_guid_1440.oss_id

kpi_definitions.name: num_samples_bad_rsrp_ta_reference
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST( kpi_cell_guid_1440.num_samples_bad_rsrp_ta, true ) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_sector_1440 inner join kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_1440 on kpi_cell_sector_1440.reference_cell = kpi_cell_guid_1440.fdn AND kpi_cell_sector_1440.cell_oss_id = kpi_cell_guid_1440.oss_id

kpi_definitions.name: num_samples_bad_rsrp_candidate
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(SUM_ARRAY_SLICE(cell_sector.num_samples_bad_rsrp_ta_candidate, kpi_cell_sector.coverage_balance_signal_range_lower_index, kpi_cell_sector.coverage_balance_signal_range_upper_index), true) FROM kpi://cell_sector inner join kpi_db://kpi_cell_sector on cell_sector.cell_fdn = kpi_cell_sector.cell_fdn AND cell_sector.cell_oss_id = kpi_cell_sector.cell_oss_id AND cell_sector.sector_id = kpi_cell_sector.sector_id

kpi_definitions.name: num_samples_bad_rsrp_reference
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(SUM_ARRAY_SLICE(cell_sector.num_samples_bad_rsrp_ta_reference, kpi_cell_sector.coverage_balance_signal_range_lower_index, kpi_cell_sector.coverage_balance_signal_range_upper_index), true) FROM kpi://cell_sector inner join kpi_db://kpi_cell_sector on cell_sector.cell_fdn = kpi_cell_sector.cell_fdn AND cell_sector.cell_oss_id = kpi_cell_sector.cell_oss_id AND cell_sector.sector_id = kpi_cell_sector.sector_id

kpi_definitions.name: percentage_bad_rsrp_samples_candidate
kpi_definitions.expression: 100 * FIRST( cell_sector.num_samples_bad_rsrp_candidate, true ) / FIRST( cell_sector.num_samples_rsrp_candidate, true ) FROM kpi://cell_sector

kpi_definitions.name: percentage_bad_rsrp_samples_reference
kpi_definitions.expression: 100 * FIRST( cell_sector.num_samples_bad_rsrp_reference, true ) / FIRST( cell_sector.num_samples_rsrp_reference, true ) FROM kpi://cell_sector

kpi_definitions.name: coverage_balance_ratio_signal
kpi_definitions.expression: 100 * FIRST( cell_sector.percentage_bad_rsrp_samples_reference, true ) / FIRST( cell_sector.percentage_bad_rsrp_samples_candidate, true ) FROM kpi://cell_sector

kpi_definitions.name: num_ue_samples_q1
kpi_definitions.expression: SUM_ARRAY_SAMPLES_PRECISION(FIRST(cell_guid.num_samples_ta_hourly, true), FIRST(0), FIRST(cell_guid.bin_q1, true), FIRST(1)) FROM kpi://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: num_ue_samples_q2
kpi_definitions.expression: SUM_ARRAY_SAMPLES_PRECISION(FIRST(cell_guid.num_samples_ta_hourly, true), FIRST(cell_guid.bin_q1, true), FIRST(cell_guid.bin_q2, true), FIRST(2)) FROM kpi://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: num_ue_samples_q3
kpi_definitions.expression: SUM_ARRAY_SAMPLES_PRECISION(FIRST(cell_guid.num_samples_ta_hourly, true), FIRST(cell_guid.bin_q2, true), FIRST(cell_guid.bin_q3, true), FIRST(3)) FROM kpi://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: num_ue_samples_q4
kpi_definitions.expression: SUM_ARRAY_SAMPLES_PRECISION(FIRST(cell_guid.num_samples_ta_hourly, true), FIRST(cell_guid.bin_q3, true), FIRST(cell_guid.bin_q4, true), FIRST(4)) FROM kpi://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: ue_total_samples_denominator
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(cell_guid.num_ue_samples_q1, true) + FIRST(cell_guid.num_ue_samples_q2, true) + FIRST(cell_guid.num_ue_samples_q3, true) + FIRST(cell_guid.num_ue_samples_q4, true) FROM kpi://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: ue_percentage_q1
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(100) * FIRST(cell_guid.num_ue_samples_q1, true) / FIRST(cell_guid.ue_total_samples_denominator, true) FROM kpi://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: ue_percentage_q2
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(100) * FIRST(cell_guid.num_ue_samples_q2, true) / FIRST(cell_guid.ue_total_samples_denominator, true) FROM kpi://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: ue_percentage_q3
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(100) * FIRST(cell_guid.num_ue_samples_q3, true) / FIRST(cell_guid.ue_total_samples_denominator, true) FROM kpi://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: ue_percentage_q4
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(100) * FIRST(cell_guid.num_ue_samples_q4, true) / FIRST(cell_guid.ue_total_samples_denominator, true) FROM kpi://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: pmpdcchcceutil_0_norm
kpi_definitions.expression: SUM(counters_cell.pmPdcchCceActivity - aggregate(slice(counters_cell.pmPdcchCceUtil, 2, 19), 0, (acc, x) -> acc + x)) FROM pm_stats://counters_cell

kpi_definitions.name: no_of_trx_points
kpi_definitions.expression: MAX(CASE WHEN sectorcarrier.noOfTrxPoints = 0 THEN 2 ELSE sectorcarrier.noOfTrxPoints END) FROM cm://sectorcarrier INNER JOIN cm://cell_sectorcarrier ON sectorcarrier.id = cell_sectorcarrier.sectorcarrier_id

kpi_definitions.name: pdcch_cfi_mode
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(CASE WHEN cell.pdcchCfiMode = ''CFI_STATIC_BY_BW'' THEN 0 WHEN cell.pdcchCfiMode = ''CFI_STATIC_1'' THEN 1 WHEN cell.pdcchCfiMode = ''CFI_STATIC_2'' THEN 2 WHEN cell.pdcchCfiMode = ''CFI_STATIC_3'' THEN 3 WHEN cell.pdcchCfiMode = ''CFI_AUTO_MAXIMUM_2'' THEN 4 WHEN cell.pdcchCfiMode = ''CFI_AUTO_MAXIMUM_3'' THEN 5 ELSE NULL END) FROM cm://cell

kpi_definitions.name: ca_adjustment_factor
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(CASE WHEN cell_guid.mac_level_data_vol_dl_rate IS NOT NULL THEN LEAST(5, cell_guid.mac_level_data_vol_dl_rate) ELSE NULL END) FROM kpi://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: pmpdcchcceutil_1_19_distribution_product
kpi_definitions.expression: SUM(counters_cell.pmPdcchCceUtil[1] * 0.075) + SUM(counters_cell.pmPdcchCceUtil[2] * 0.125) + SUM(counters_cell.pmPdcchCceUtil[3] * 0.175) + SUM(counters_cell.pmPdcchCceUtil[4] * 0.225) + SUM(counters_cell.pmPdcchCceUtil[5] * 0.275) + SUM(counters_cell.pmPdcchCceUtil[6] * 0.325) + SUM(counters_cell.pmPdcchCceUtil[7] * 0.375) + SUM(counters_cell.pmPdcchCceUtil[8] * 0.425) + SUM(counters_cell.pmPdcchCceUtil[9] * 0.475) + SUM(counters_cell.pmPdcchCceUtil[10] * 0.525) + SUM(counters_cell.pmPdcchCceUtil[11] * 0.575) + SUM(counters_cell.pmPdcchCceUtil[12] * 0.625) + SUM(counters_cell.pmPdcchCceUtil[13] * 0.675) + SUM(counters_cell.pmPdcchCceUtil[14] * 0.725) + SUM(counters_cell.pmPdcchCceUtil[15] * 0.775) + SUM(counters_cell.pmPdcchCceUtil[16] * 0.825) + SUM(counters_cell.pmPdcchCceUtil[17] * 0.875) + SUM(counters_cell.pmPdcchCceUtil[18] * 0.925) + SUM(counters_cell.pmPdcchCceUtil[19] *  0.975) FROM pm_stats://counters_cell

kpi_definitions.name: resource_elements_per_prb_mode_4
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(CASE WHEN cell_guid.resource_elements_per_prb_interim_mode_4_5 IS NOT NULL THEN GREATEST(LEAST(141.8, cell_guid.resource_elements_per_prb_interim_mode_4_5), 129.8) ELSE NULL END) FROM kpi://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: resource_elements_per_prb_mode_5
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(CASE WHEN cell_guid.resource_elements_per_prb_interim_mode_4_5 IS NOT NULL THEN GREATEST(LEAST(141.8, cell_guid.resource_elements_per_prb_interim_mode_4_5), 117.8) ELSE NULL END) FROM kpi://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: resource_elements_per_prb
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(CASE WHEN cell_guid.pdcch_cfi_mode = 0 AND cell_guid.bandwidth > 10000 THEN 141.8 WHEN cell_guid.pdcch_cfi_mode = 0 AND cell_guid.bandwidth <= 10000 THEN 129.8 WHEN cell_guid.pdcch_cfi_mode = 1 THEN 141.8 WHEN cell_guid.pdcch_cfi_mode = 2 THEN 129.8 WHEN cell_guid.pdcch_cfi_mode = 3 THEN 117.8 WHEN cell_guid.pdcch_cfi_mode = 4 THEN cell_guid.resource_elements_per_prb_mode_4  WHEN cell_guid.pdcch_cfi_mode = 5 THEN cell_guid.resource_elements_per_prb_mode_5 END) FROM kpi://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: active_ues_mbb
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(CASE WHEN (cell_guid.active_ues_dl) < (cell_guid.active_ues_volte_dl) THEN (cell_guid.active_ues_dl) ELSE (cell_guid.active_ues_dl) - (cell_guid.active_ues_volte_dl) END) FROM kpi://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: cqi
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(CASE WHEN cell_guid.double_count_factor_radio_tx_rank_distr IS NULL THEN NULL ELSE CONCAT(ZIP_WITH(cell_guid.cqi1 , TRANSFORM(cell_guid.cqi2 , x -> x * cell_guid.double_count_factor_radio_tx_rank_distr), (cqi1Value,cCqi2Value) -> if (cqi1Value-cCqi2Value < 0, 0, cqi1Value-cCqi2Value)),TRANSFORM(cell_guid.cqi2 , x -> x * cell_guid.double_count_factor_radio_tx_rank_distr)) END) FROM kpi://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: achievable_throughput_dist
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(CASE WHEN cell_guid.interim_kpi_prbs_and_elements_per_user IS NULL THEN NULL ELSE TRANSFORM(array(0.152, 0.234, 0.377, 0.602, 0.877, 1.176, 1.477, 1.914, 2.406, 2.730, 3.322, 3.902, 4.523, 5.115, 5.555, 0.305, 0.469, 0.754, 1.203, 1.754, 2.352, 2.953, 3.828, 4.812, 5.461, 6.645, 7.805, 9.047, 10.230, 11.109), x -> x * cell_guid.interim_kpi_prbs_and_elements_per_user) END) FROM kpi://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: cqi_sum
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(aggregate(cell_guid.cqi, double(0), (acc, x) -> acc + x)) FROM kpi://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: connected_users_with_execution_id
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(kpi_cell_guid_60.connected_users) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60 INNER JOIN flm://cell_configuration ON kpi_cell_guid_60.fdn = cell_configuration.fdn AND kpi_cell_guid_60.oss_id = cell_configuration.oss_id

kpi_definitions.name: achievable_throughput_indicator_array
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(TRANSFORM(kpi_cell_guid_60.achievable_throughput_dist,  x -> if (x < cell_guid_flm.target_throughput_r, 1, 0))) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60 inner join kpi://cell_guid_flm on kpi_cell_guid_60.fdn = cell_guid_flm.fdn AND kpi_cell_guid_60.oss_id = cell_guid_flm.oss_id

kpi_definitions.name: p_failing_r_mbps_numerator_array
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(ZIP_WITH(kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.achievable_throughput_indicator_array, kpi_cell_guid_60.cqi, (l, m) -> (l * m))) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_flm_60 inner join kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60 on kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.fdn = kpi_cell_guid_60.fdn AND kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.oss_id = kpi_cell_guid_60.oss_id AND kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.local_timestamp = kpi_cell_guid_60.local_timestamp

kpi_definitions.name: p_failing_r_mbps_numerator
kpi_definitions.expression: SUM(aggregate(cell_guid_flm.p_failing_r_mbps_numerator_array, double(0), (acc, x) -> acc + x)) FROM kpi://cell_guid_flm

kpi_definitions.name: p_failing_r_mbps
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.p_failing_r_mbps_numerator) / FIRST(kpi_cell_guid_60.cqi_sum) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_flm_60 inner join kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60 on kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.fdn = kpi_cell_guid_60.fdn AND kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.oss_id = kpi_cell_guid_60.oss_id AND kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.local_timestamp = kpi_cell_guid_60.local_timestamp

kpi_definitions.name: unhappy_users
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.p_failing_r_mbps) * FIRST(kpi_cell_guid_60.connected_users) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_flm_60 inner join kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60 on kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.fdn = kpi_cell_guid_60.fdn AND kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.oss_id = kpi_cell_guid_60.oss_id AND kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.local_timestamp = kpi_cell_guid_60.local_timestamp

kpi_definitions.name: num_calls_cell_sector_hourly
kpi_definitions.expression: SUM(cell_guid.num_calls_cell_hourly) FROM kpi://cell_guid  INNER JOIN cm://cell_sector ON cell_guid.fdn = cell_sector.cell_fdn AND cell_guid.oss_id = cell_sector.cell_oss_id

kpi_definitions.name: sector_busy_hour
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(kpi_sector_60.local_timestamp, true) FROM kpi://sector LEFT JOIN kpi_db://kpi_sector_60 ON sector.sector_id = kpi_sector_60.sector_id WHERE kpi_sector_60.num_calls_sector_hourly = sector.sector_busy_hour_indicator

kpi_definitions.name: e_rab_retainability_percentage_lost_qci1
kpi_definitions.expression: 100 * ( FIRST(cell_guid.pm_erab_rel_abnormal_enb_act_qci1, true) + FIRST(cell_guid.pm_erab_rel_abnormal_mme_act_qci1, true) ) / ( FIRST(cell_guid.pm_erab_rel_abnormal_enb_qci1, true) + FIRST(cell_guid.pm_erab_rel_normal_enb_qci1, true) + FIRST(cell_guid.pm_erab_rel_mme_qci1, true) )  FROM kpi_post_agg://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: pm_rrc_conn_estab_fail_mme_ovl_mos
kpi_definitions.expression: CASE WHEN SUM(counters_cell.pmRrcConnEstabFailMmeOvlMos) IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE SUM(counters_cell.pmRrcConnEstabFailMmeOvlMos) END FROM pm_stats://counters_cell

kpi_definitions.name: pm_rrc_conn_estab_fail_mme_ovl_mod
kpi_definitions.expression: CASE WHEN SUM(counters_cell.pmRrcConnEstabFailMmeOvlMod) IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE SUM(counters_cell.pmRrcConnEstabFailMmeOvlMod) END FROM pm_stats://counters_cell

kpi_definitions.name: pm_s1_sig_conn_estab_fail_mme_ovl_mos
kpi_definitions.expression: CASE WHEN SUM(counters_cell.pmS1SigConnEstabFailMmeOvlMos) IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE SUM(counters_cell.pmS1SigConnEstabFailMmeOvlMos) END FROM pm_stats://counters_cell

kpi_definitions.name: initial_and_added_e_rab_establishment_sr
kpi_definitions.expression: 100 * ((FIRST( cell_guid.pm_rrc_conn_estab_succ, true ) * 0.01) * (FIRST( cell_guid.pm_s1_sig_conn_estab_succ, true) * 0.01) * ((FIRST( cell_guid.num_calls_daily, true ) * 0.01) + (FIRST( cell_guid.pm_erab_estab_succ_added, true ) * 0.01))) / (((FIRST( cell_guid.pm_rrc_conn_estab_att, true ) * 0.01) - (FIRST( cell_guid.pm_rrc_conn_estab_att_reatt, true ) * 0.01) - (FIRST( cell_guid.pm_rrc_conn_estab_fail_mme_ovl_mos, true ) * 0.01) - (FIRST( cell_guid.pm_rrc_conn_estab_fail_mme_ovl_mod, true ) * 0.01)) * ((FIRST( cell_guid.pm_s1_sig_conn_estab_att, true ) * 0.01) - (FIRST( cell_guid.pm_s1_sig_conn_estab_fail_mme_ovl_mos, true ) * 0.01)) * ((FIRST( cell_guid.pm_erab_estab_att_init, true ) * 0.01) + (FIRST( cell_guid.pm_erab_estab_att_added, true ) * 0.01) - (FIRST( cell_guid.pm_erab_estab_att_added_ho_ongoing, true ) * 0.01))) FROM kpi_post_agg://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: rrc_conn_estab_att_int
kpi_definitions.expression: SUM(counters_cell.pmRrcConnEstabAttMod + counters_cell.pmRrcConnEstabAttMoVoice + counters_cell.pmRrcConnEstabAttMta + counters_cell.pmRrcConnEstabAttHpa - COALESCE( counters_cell.pmRrcConnEstabFailMmeOvlMod , 0))  FROM pm_stats://counters_cell

kpi_definitions.name: cell_prep_att
kpi_definitions.expression: CASE WHEN SUM(counters_cell.pmHoPrepRejOutUlThres) IS NULL THEN (SUM(counters_cell.pmCellHoPrepAttLteIntraF) + SUM(counters_cell.pmCellHoPrepAttLteInterF)) ELSE(SUM(counters_cell.pmCellHoPrepAttLteIntraF) + SUM(counters_cell.pmCellHoPrepAttLteInterF) - SUM(counters_cell.pmHoPrepRejOutUlThres)) END FROM pm_stats://counters_cell

kpi_definitions.name: mcu_cdf
kpi_definitions.expression: array_sort(collect_list(ROUND(kpi_cell_guid_60.connected_users,2))) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60 JOIN kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_flm_60 ON kpi_cell_guid_60.local_timestamp = kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.local_timestamp AND kpi_cell_guid_60.fdn = kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.fdn AND kpi_cell_guid_60.oss_id = kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.oss_id WHERE ROUND(kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.p_failing_r_mbps, 1) = ${param.qos_for_capacity_estimation}

kpi_definitions.name: execution_sector_busy_hour
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(kpi_sector_1440.sector_busy_hour) FROM kpi_db://kpi_sector_1440 INNER JOIN flm://cell_configuration ON kpi_sector_1440.sector_id = cell_configuration.sector_id

kpi_definitions.name: actual_connected_users
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(kpi_cell_guid_60.connected_users) FROM kpi://cell_sector_flm JOIN kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60 ON cell_sector_flm.cell_id = kpi_cell_guid_60.guid AND cell_sector_flm.cell_fdn = kpi_cell_guid_60.fdn AND cell_sector_flm.cell_oss_id = kpi_cell_guid_60.oss_id AND cell_sector_flm.execution_sector_busy_hour = kpi_cell_guid_60.local_timestamp

kpi_definitions.name: freq_band_daily
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(kpi_cell_guid_60.freq_band) FROM kpi://cell_sector_flm JOIN kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60 ON cell_sector_flm.cell_id = kpi_cell_guid_60.guid AND cell_sector_flm.cell_fdn = kpi_cell_guid_60.fdn AND cell_sector_flm.cell_oss_id = kpi_cell_guid_60.oss_id AND cell_sector_flm.execution_sector_busy_hour = kpi_cell_guid_60.local_timestamp

kpi_definitions.name: bandwidth_daily
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(kpi_cell_guid_60.bandwidth) FROM kpi://cell_sector_flm JOIN kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60 ON cell_sector_flm.cell_id = kpi_cell_guid_60.guid AND cell_sector_flm.cell_fdn = kpi_cell_guid_60.fdn AND cell_sector_flm.cell_oss_id = kpi_cell_guid_60.oss_id AND cell_sector_flm.execution_sector_busy_hour = kpi_cell_guid_60.local_timestamp

kpi_definitions.name: target_throughput_r_daily
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.target_throughput_r) FROM kpi://cell_sector_flm JOIN kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_flm_60 ON cell_sector_flm.cell_id = kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.guid AND cell_sector_flm.cell_fdn = kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.fdn AND cell_sector_flm.cell_oss_id = kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.oss_id AND cell_sector_flm.execution_sector_busy_hour = kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.local_timestamp

kpi_definitions.name: max_connected_users_daily
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(kpi_freqband_bandwidth_r_flm_1440.max_connected_users) FROM kpi://cell_sector_flm JOIN kpi_db://kpi_freqband_bandwidth_r_flm_1440 ON cell_sector_flm.freq_band_daily = kpi_freqband_bandwidth_r_flm_1440.freq_band AND cell_sector_flm.bandwidth_daily = kpi_freqband_bandwidth_r_flm_1440.bandwidth AND cell_sector_flm.target_throughput_r_daily = kpi_freqband_bandwidth_r_flm_1440.target_throughput_r

kpi_definitions.name: num_values_used_for_mcu_cdf_calculation_daily
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(kpi_freqband_bandwidth_r_flm_1440.num_values_used_for_mcu_cdf_calculation) FROM kpi://cell_sector_flm JOIN kpi_db://kpi_freqband_bandwidth_r_flm_1440 ON cell_sector_flm.freq_band_daily = kpi_freqband_bandwidth_r_flm_1440.freq_band AND cell_sector_flm.bandwidth_daily = kpi_freqband_bandwidth_r_flm_1440.bandwidth AND cell_sector_flm.target_throughput_r_daily = kpi_freqband_bandwidth_r_flm_1440.target_throughput_r

kpi_definitions.name: pm_ue_throughput_vol_ul
kpi_definitions.expression: SUM(counters_cell.pmUeThpVolUl) FROM pm_stats://counters_cell INNER JOIN cm://cell_sector ON counters_cell.fdn = cell_sector.cell_fdn AND counters_cell.oss_id = cell_sector.cell_oss_id

kpi_definitions.name: pm_ue_throughput_time_ul
kpi_definitions.expression: SUM(counters_cell.pmUeThpTimeUl) FROM pm_stats://counters_cell INNER JOIN cm://cell_sector ON counters_cell.fdn = cell_sector.cell_fdn AND counters_cell.oss_id = cell_sector.cell_oss_id

kpi_definitions.name: cell_prep_att_hourly
kpi_definitions.expression: CASE WHEN SUM(counters_cell.pmHoPrepRejOutUlThres) IS NULL THEN (SUM(counters_cell.pmCellHoPrepAttLteIntraF) + SUM(counters_cell.pmCellHoPrepAttLteInterF)) ELSE(SUM(counters_cell.pmCellHoPrepAttLteIntraF) + SUM(counters_cell.pmCellHoPrepAttLteInterF) - SUM(counters_cell.pmHoPrepRejOutUlThres)) END FROM pm_stats://counters_cell

kpi_definitions.name: pm_ue_throughput_vol_minus_lasttti_dl
kpi_definitions.expression: SUM(counters_cell.pmPdcpVolDlDrb - counters_cell.pmPdcpVolDlDrbLastTTI) FROM pm_stats://counters_cell INNER JOIN cm://cell_sector ON counters_cell.fdn = cell_sector.cell_fdn AND counters_cell.oss_id = cell_sector.cell_oss_id

kpi_definitions.name: pm_ue_throughput_time_dl
kpi_definitions.expression: SUM(counters_cell.pmUeThpTimeDl) FROM pm_stats://counters_cell INNER JOIN cm://cell_sector ON counters_cell.fdn = cell_sector.cell_fdn AND counters_cell.oss_id = cell_sector.cell_oss_id

kpi_definitions.name: rrc_conn_estab_att_hourly
kpi_definitions.expression: SUM(counters_cell.pmRrcConnEstabAtt - counters_cell.pmRrcConnEstabAttReatt - COALESCE( counters_cell.pmRrcConnEstabFailMmeOvlMos , 0) - COALESCE( counters_cell.pmRrcConnEstabFailMmeOvlMod , 0)) FROM pm_stats://counters_cell

kpi_definitions.name: initial_and_added_e_rab_establishment_sr_hourly
kpi_definitions.expression: (100 * FIRST(cell_guid.pm_rrc_conn_estab_succ_hourly, true) * FIRST(cell_guid.pm_s1_sig_conn_estab_succ_hourly, true) * FIRST(cell_guid.erab_estab_succ_hourly, true)) / (FIRST(cell_guid.rrc_conn_estab_att_hourly, true) * FIRST(cell_guid.s1_sig_conn_estab_att_hourly, true) * FIRST(cell_guid.erab_estab_att_hourly, true)) FROM kpi://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: rrc_conn_estab_succ_hourly
kpi_definitions.expression: SUM(counters_cell.pmRrcConnEstabSuccMod + counters_cell.pmRrcConnEstabSuccMoVoice + counters_cell.pmRrcConnEstabSuccMta + counters_cell.pmRrcConnEstabSuccHpa) FROM pm_stats://counters_cell

kpi_definitions.name: s1_sig_conn_estab_succ_hourly
kpi_definitions.expression: SUM(counters_cell.pmS1SigConnEstabSuccMod + counters_cell.pmS1SigConnEstabSuccMoVoice +  counters_cell.pmS1SigConnEstabSuccMta + counters_cell.pmS1SigConnEstabSuccHpa) FROM pm_stats://counters_cell

kpi_definitions.name: rrc_conn_estab_att_int_hourly
kpi_definitions.expression: SUM( counters_cell.pmRrcConnEstabAttMod + counters_cell.pmRrcConnEstabAttMoVoice + counters_cell.pmRrcConnEstabAttMta + counters_cell.pmRrcConnEstabAttHpa - counters_cell.pmRrcConnEstabAttReattMod - counters_cell.pmRrcConnEstabAttReattMoVoice - counters_cell.pmRrcConnEstabAttReattMta - counters_cell.pmRrcConnEstabAttReattHpa - COALESCE( counters_cell.pmRrcConnEstabFailMmeOvlMod , 0))  FROM pm_stats://counters_cell

kpi_definitions.name: s1_sig_conn_estab_attm_hourly
kpi_definitions.expression: SUM(counters_cell.pmS1SigConnEstabAttMod + counters_cell.pmS1SigConnEstabAttMoVoice +  counters_cell.pmS1SigConnEstabAttMta + counters_cell.pmS1SigConnEstabAttHpa) FROM pm_stats://counters_cell

kpi_definitions.name: p_failing_r_mbps_previous
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.p_failing_r_mbps) FROM kpi://cell_guid_flm JOIN kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_flm_60 ON kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.fdn = cell_guid_flm.fdn AND kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.oss_id = cell_guid_flm.oss_id AND kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.target_throughput_r = cell_guid_flm.target_throughput_r AND EXTRACT(hour from kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.local_timestamp) = EXTRACT(hour from cell_guid_flm.local_timestamp)

kpi_definitions.name: app_coverage_reliability
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(CASE WHEN kpi_cell_guid_60.counter_cell_reliability_hourly >= cell_guid_flm.min_rops_for_app_cov_reliability AND kpi_cell_guid_60.cqi_sum >= cell_guid_flm.min_num_cqi_samples AND kpi_cell_guid_60.num_non_null_counters_count_app_coverage = counter_cell_reliability_hourly * 15 THEN true ELSE false END) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60 INNER JOIN kpi://cell_guid_flm ON kpi_cell_guid_60.fdn = cell_guid_flm.fdn AND kpi_cell_guid_60.oss_id = cell_guid_flm.oss_id

kpi_definitions.name: hourly_detrended_array
kpi_definitions.expression: collect_list(cell_guid_flm.p_failing_r_mbps_detrended) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_flm_60 join kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_flm_60 as cell_guid_flm ON kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.oss_id = cell_guid_flm.oss_id AND kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.fdn = cell_guid_flm.fdn AND cell_guid_flm.local_timestamp between kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.local_timestamp - interval 1 hour AND kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.local_timestamp + interval 1 hour AND date_trunc(''Day'', cell_guid_flm.local_timestamp) = date_trunc(''Day'', kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.local_timestamp) AND cell_guid_flm.p_failing_r_mbps_detrended IS NOT NULL

kpi_definitions.name: num_detrended_rolling_array
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(APPEND_INTEGER_ARRAY(CASE WHEN cell_guid_flm.num_detrended_rolling_array IS NULL THEN cell_guid_flm.num_hourly_detrended_array ELSE cell_guid_flm.num_detrended_rolling_array END, kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.num_hourly_detrended_array, ${param.transient_num_days}+1), true) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_flm_60 join kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_flm_60 as cell_guid_flm ON kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.oss_id = cell_guid_flm.oss_id AND kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.fdn = cell_guid_flm.fdn AND extract(hour from kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.local_timestamp) = (extract(hour from cell_guid_flm.local_timestamp)) AND cell_guid_flm.local_timestamp < kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.local_timestamp AND kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.target_throughput_r = cell_guid_flm.target_throughput_r

kpi_definitions.name: detrended_rolling_array
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(APPEND_DOUBLE_ARRAY_GIVEN_CARDINALITY_AND_LIMIT(cell_guid_flm.detrended_rolling_array, cell_guid_flm.hourly_detrended_array, kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.num_detrended_rolling_array, ${param.transient_num_days}), true) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_flm_60 join kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_flm_60 as cell_guid_flm ON kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.oss_id = cell_guid_flm.oss_id AND kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.fdn = cell_guid_flm.fdn AND extract(hour from kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.local_timestamp) = (extract(hour from cell_guid_flm.local_timestamp)) AND cell_guid_flm.local_timestamp < kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.local_timestamp AND kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.target_throughput_r = cell_guid_flm.target_throughput_r

kpi_definitions.name: detrended_probability_array
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(CASE WHEN kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.detrended_rolling_array IS NULL THEN kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.hourly_detrended_array ELSE (kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.detrended_rolling_array || kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.hourly_detrended_array) END, true) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_flm_60

kpi_definitions.name: detrended_probability_array_daily
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.detrended_probability_array) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_flm_60 JOIN kpi_db://kpi_cell_sector_flm_1440 ON kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.fdn = kpi_cell_sector_flm_1440.cell_fdn AND kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.oss_id = kpi_cell_sector_flm_1440.cell_oss_id and kpi_cell_guid_flm_60.local_timestamp = kpi_cell_sector_flm_1440.execution_sector_busy_hour

kpi_definitions.name: num_samp_trans_calc
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(CASE WHEN cell_sector_flm.detrended_probability_array_daily IS NULL THEN NULL ELSE cardinality(cell_sector_flm.detrended_probability_array_daily) END) FROM kpi://cell_sector_flm

kpi_definitions.name: alternate_sigma
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(( (cell_sector_flm.num_samp_trans_calc) * (kpi_cell_guid_flm_1440.sigma_for_transient) + 6.0)) / FIRST(cell_sector_flm.num_samp_trans_calc) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_flm_1440 JOIN kpi://cell_sector_flm ON kpi_cell_guid_flm_1440.guid = cell_sector_flm.cell_id AND kpi_cell_guid_flm_1440.fdn = cell_sector_flm.cell_fdn AND kpi_cell_guid_flm_1440.oss_id = cell_sector_flm.cell_oss_id

kpi_definitions.name: final_sigma
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(CASE WHEN cell_sector_flm.num_samp_trans_calc IS NULL THEN NULL WHEN cell_sector_flm.num_samp_trans_calc >= kpi_cell_guid_flm_1440.min_num_samp_trans_calc THEN kpi_cell_guid_flm_1440.sigma_for_transient ELSE cell_sector_flm.alternate_sigma END) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_flm_1440 JOIN kpi://cell_sector_flm ON kpi_cell_guid_flm_1440.guid = cell_sector_flm.cell_id AND kpi_cell_guid_flm_1440.fdn = cell_sector_flm.cell_fdn AND kpi_cell_guid_flm_1440.oss_id = cell_sector_flm.cell_oss_id

kpi_definitions.name: cell_handover_success_rate_hourly_rss
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(ADD_DOUBLE_TO_ARRAY_WITH_LIMIT(cell_guid.cell_handover_success_rate_hourly_rss, kpi_cell_guid_60.cell_handover_success_rate_hourly, 8)) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60 LEFT JOIN kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60 as cell_guid ON kpi_cell_guid_60.guid = cell_guid.guid AND kpi_cell_guid_60.oss_id = cell_guid.oss_id AND kpi_cell_guid_60.fdn = cell_guid.fdn AND cell_guid.local_timestamp = (kpi_cell_guid_60.local_timestamp - interval 1 day) WHERE kpi_cell_guid_60.cell_handover_success_rate_hourly_rss IS NULL
filter: kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60.utc_timestamp BETWEEN (date_trunc(''hour'', TO_TIMESTAMP(''${param.start_date_time}'')) - interval 1 day) and date_trunc(''hour'', TO_TIMESTAMP(''${param.end_date_time}''))

kpi_definitions.name: initial_and_added_e_rab_establishment_sr_hourly_rss
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(ADD_DOUBLE_TO_ARRAY_WITH_LIMIT(cell_guid.initial_and_added_e_rab_establishment_sr_hourly_rss, kpi_cell_guid_60.initial_and_added_e_rab_establishment_sr_hourly, 8)) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60 LEFT JOIN kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60 as cell_guid ON kpi_cell_guid_60.guid = cell_guid.guid AND kpi_cell_guid_60.oss_id = cell_guid.oss_id AND kpi_cell_guid_60.fdn = cell_guid.fdn AND cell_guid.local_timestamp = (kpi_cell_guid_60.local_timestamp - interval 1 day) WHERE kpi_cell_guid_60.initial_and_added_e_rab_establishment_sr_hourly_rss IS NULL
filter: kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60.utc_timestamp BETWEEN (date_trunc(''hour'', TO_TIMESTAMP(''${param.start_date_time}'')) - interval 1 day) and date_trunc(''hour'', TO_TIMESTAMP(''${param.end_date_time}''))

kpi_definitions.name: initial_and_added_e_rab_establishment_sr_qci1_hourly_rss
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(ADD_DOUBLE_TO_ARRAY_WITH_LIMIT(cell_guid.initial_and_added_e_rab_establishment_sr_qci1_hourly_rss, kpi_cell_guid_60.initial_and_added_e_rab_establishment_sr_for_qci1_hourly, 8)) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60 LEFT JOIN kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60 as cell_guid ON kpi_cell_guid_60.guid = cell_guid.guid AND kpi_cell_guid_60.oss_id = cell_guid.oss_id AND kpi_cell_guid_60.fdn = cell_guid.fdn AND cell_guid.local_timestamp = (kpi_cell_guid_60.local_timestamp - interval 1 day) WHERE kpi_cell_guid_60.initial_and_added_e_rab_establishment_sr_qci1_hourly_rss IS NULL
filter: kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60.utc_timestamp BETWEEN (date_trunc(''hour'', TO_TIMESTAMP(''${param.start_date_time}'')) - interval 1 day) and date_trunc(''hour'', TO_TIMESTAMP(''${param.end_date_time}''))

kpi_definitions.name: e_rab_retainability_percentage_lost_hourly_rss
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(ADD_DOUBLE_TO_ARRAY_WITH_LIMIT(cell_guid.e_rab_retainability_percentage_lost_hourly_rss, kpi_cell_guid_60.e_rab_retainability_percentage_lost_hourly, 8)) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60 LEFT JOIN kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60 as cell_guid ON kpi_cell_guid_60.guid = cell_guid.guid AND kpi_cell_guid_60.oss_id = cell_guid.oss_id AND kpi_cell_guid_60.fdn = cell_guid.fdn AND cell_guid.local_timestamp = (kpi_cell_guid_60.local_timestamp - interval 1 day) WHERE kpi_cell_guid_60.e_rab_retainability_percentage_lost_hourly_rss IS NULL
filter: kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60.utc_timestamp BETWEEN (date_trunc(''hour'', TO_TIMESTAMP(''${param.start_date_time}'')) - interval 1 day) and date_trunc(''hour'', TO_TIMESTAMP(''${param.end_date_time}''))

kpi_definitions.name: e_rab_retainability_percentage_lost_qci1_hourly_rss
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(ADD_DOUBLE_TO_ARRAY_WITH_LIMIT(cell_guid.e_rab_retainability_percentage_lost_qci1_hourly_rss, kpi_cell_guid_60.e_rab_retainability_percentage_lost_qci1_hourly, 8)) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60 LEFT JOIN kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60 as cell_guid ON kpi_cell_guid_60.guid = cell_guid.guid AND kpi_cell_guid_60.oss_id = cell_guid.oss_id AND kpi_cell_guid_60.fdn = cell_guid.fdn AND cell_guid.local_timestamp = (kpi_cell_guid_60.local_timestamp - interval 1 day) WHERE kpi_cell_guid_60.e_rab_retainability_percentage_lost_qci1_hourly_rss IS NULL
filter: kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60.utc_timestamp BETWEEN (date_trunc(''hour'', TO_TIMESTAMP(''${param.start_date_time}'')) - interval 1 day) and date_trunc(''hour'', TO_TIMESTAMP(''${param.end_date_time}''))

kpi_definitions.name: avg_ul_pdcp_throughput_sector_rss
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(ADD_DOUBLE_TO_ARRAY_WITH_LIMIT(sector.avg_ul_pdcp_throughput_sector_rss, kpi_sector_60.avg_ul_pdcp_throughput_sector, 8)) FROM kpi_db://kpi_sector_60 LEFT JOIN kpi_db://kpi_sector_60 as sector ON kpi_sector_60.sector_id = sector.sector_id AND sector.local_timestamp = (kpi_sector_60.local_timestamp - interval 1 day) WHERE kpi_sector_60.avg_ul_pdcp_throughput_sector_rss IS NULL
filter: kpi_db://kpi_sector_60.utc_timestamp BETWEEN (date_trunc(''hour'', TO_TIMESTAMP(''${param.start_date_time}'')) - interval 1 day) and date_trunc(''hour'', TO_TIMESTAMP(''${param.end_date_time}''))

kpi_definitions.name: avg_dl_pdcp_throughput_sector_rss
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(ADD_DOUBLE_TO_ARRAY_WITH_LIMIT(sector.avg_dl_pdcp_throughput_sector_rss, kpi_sector_60.avg_dl_pdcp_throughput_sector, 8)) FROM kpi_db://kpi_sector_60 LEFT JOIN kpi_db://kpi_sector_60 as sector ON kpi_sector_60.sector_id = sector.sector_id AND sector.local_timestamp = (kpi_sector_60.local_timestamp - interval 1 day) WHERE kpi_sector_60.avg_dl_pdcp_throughput_sector_rss IS NULL
filter: kpi_db://kpi_sector_60.utc_timestamp BETWEEN (date_trunc(''hour'', TO_TIMESTAMP(''${param.start_date_time}'')) - interval 1 day) and date_trunc(''hour'', TO_TIMESTAMP(''${param.end_date_time}''))

kpi_definitions.name: cell_handover_success_rate_degradation
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(DEGRADATION_THRESHOLD(''MAX'', 0, kpi_cell_guid_60.cell_handover_success_rate_hourly_rss, ''${param.cell_handover_success_rate_confidence_interval}'', ''${param.weekend_days}'', date_trunc(''day'', kpi_cell_guid_60.local_timestamp), 8, true)) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60 JOIN flm://cell_configuration_history ON cell_configuration_history.fdn = kpi_cell_guid_60.fdn AND cell_configuration_history.oss_id = kpi_cell_guid_60.oss_id

kpi_definitions.name: initial_and_added_e_rab_estab_sr_degradation

kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(DEGRADATION_THRESHOLD(''MAX'', 0, kpi_cell_guid_60.initial_and_added_e_rab_establishment_sr_qci1_hourly_rss, ''${param.initial_and_added_e_rab_estab_sr_qci1_hourly_confidence_interval}'', ''${param.weekend_days}'', date_trunc(''day'', kpi_cell_guid_60.local_timestamp), 8, true)) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60 JOIN flm://cell_configuration_history ON cell_configuration_history.fdn = kpi_cell_guid_60.fdn AND cell_configuration_history.oss_id = kpi_cell_guid_60.oss_id

kpi_definitions.name: e_rab_retainability_percentage_lost_qci1_degradation
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(DEGRADATION_THRESHOLD(''MIN'', 100, kpi_cell_guid_60.e_rab_retainability_percentage_lost_qci1_hourly_rss, ''${param.e_rab_retainability_percentage_lost_qci1_hourly_confidence_interval}'', ''${param.weekend_days}'', date_trunc(''day'', kpi_cell_guid_60.local_timestamp), 8, false)) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60 JOIN flm://cell_configuration_history ON cell_configuration_history.fdn = kpi_cell_guid_60.fdn AND cell_configuration_history.oss_id = kpi_cell_guid_60.oss_id

kpi_definitions.name: avg_ul_pdcp_throughput_sector_interim_degradation
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(cell_guid_flm.e_rab_retainability_percentage_lost_qci1_degradation) FROM kpi://cell_guid_flm JOIN cm://cell_sector ON cell_guid_flm.guid = cell_sector.cell_id

kpi_definitions.name: avg_ul_pdcp_throughput_sector_degradation
kpi_definitions.expression: CALCULATE_AFTER_FLOAT(FIRST(cell_sector_flm.avg_ul_pdcp_throughput_sector_interim_degradation)) + FIRST(DEGRADATION_THRESHOLD(''MAX'', 0, kpi_sector_60.avg_ul_pdcp_throughput_sector_rss, ''${param.avg_ul_pdcp_throughput_sector_confidence_interval}'', ''${param.weekend_days}'', date_trunc(''day'', kpi_sector_60.local_timestamp), 8, true)) FROM kpi_db://kpi_sector_60 JOIN kpi://cell_sector_flm ON cell_sector_flm.sector_id = kpi_sector_60.sector_id

kpi_definitions.name: avg_dl_pdcp_throughput_sector_interim_degradation
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(cell_guid_flm.e_rab_retainability_percentage_lost_qci1_degradation) FROM kpi://cell_guid_flm JOIN cm://cell_sector ON cell_guid_flm.guid = cell_sector.cell_id

kpi_definitions.name: avg_dl_pdcp_throughput_sector_degradation
kpi_definitions.expression: CALCULATE_AFTER_FLOAT(FIRST(cell_sector_flm.avg_dl_pdcp_throughput_sector_interim_degradation)) + FIRST(DEGRADATION_THRESHOLD(''MAX'', 0, kpi_sector_60.avg_dl_pdcp_throughput_sector_rss, ''${param.avg_dl_pdcp_throughput_sector_confidence_interval}'', ''${param.weekend_days}'', date_trunc(''day'', kpi_sector_60.local_timestamp), 8, true)) FROM kpi_db://kpi_sector_60 JOIN kpi://cell_sector_flm ON cell_sector_flm.sector_id = kpi_sector_60.sector_id

kpi_definitions.name: num_samples_rsrp_ta_q1
kpi_definitions.expression: SUM_ARRAY_SAMPLES_PRECISION(FIRST(cell_guid.num_samples_rsrp_ta_hourly, true), FIRST(0), FIRST(cell_guid.bin_q1, true), FIRST(1)) FROM kpi://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: num_samples_rsrp_ta_q2
kpi_definitions.expression: SUM_ARRAY_SAMPLES_PRECISION(FIRST(cell_guid.num_samples_rsrp_ta_hourly, true), FIRST(cell_guid.bin_q1, true), FIRST(cell_guid.bin_q2, true), FIRST(2)) FROM kpi://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: num_samples_rsrp_ta_q4
kpi_definitions.expression: SUM_ARRAY_SAMPLES_PRECISION(FIRST(cell_guid.num_samples_rsrp_ta_hourly, true), FIRST(cell_guid.bin_q3, true), FIRST(cell_guid.bin_q4, true), FIRST(4)) FROM kpi://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: num_bad_samples_rsrp_ta_q1
kpi_definitions.expression: SUM_ARRAY_SAMPLES_PRECISION(FIRST(cell_guid.num_samples_bad_rsrp_ta_hourly, true), FIRST(0), FIRST(cell_guid.bin_q1, true), FIRST(1)) FROM kpi://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: num_bad_samples_rsrp_ta_q2
kpi_definitions.expression: SUM_ARRAY_SAMPLES_PRECISION(FIRST(cell_guid.num_samples_bad_rsrp_ta_hourly, true), FIRST(cell_guid.bin_q1, true), FIRST(cell_guid.bin_q2, true), FIRST(2)) FROM kpi://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: num_bad_samples_rsrp_ta_q4
kpi_definitions.expression: SUM_ARRAY_SAMPLES_PRECISION(FIRST(cell_guid.num_samples_bad_rsrp_ta_hourly, true), FIRST(cell_guid.bin_q3, true), FIRST(cell_guid.bin_q4, true), FIRST(4)) FROM kpi://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: bad_rsrp_percentage_q1
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(100) * FIRST(cell_guid.num_bad_samples_rsrp_ta_q1, true) / FIRST(cell_guid.num_samples_rsrp_ta_q1, true) FROM kpi://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: bad_rsrp_percentage_q2
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(100) * FIRST(cell_guid.num_bad_samples_rsrp_ta_q2, true) / FIRST(cell_guid.num_samples_rsrp_ta_q2, true) FROM kpi://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: bad_rsrp_percentage_q3

kpi_definitions.name: bad_rsrp_percentage_q4
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(100) * FIRST(cell_guid.num_bad_samples_rsrp_ta_q4, true) / FIRST(cell_guid.num_samples_rsrp_ta_q4, true) FROM kpi://cell_guid

kpi_definitions.name: ul_pusch_sinr_hourly_numerator
kpi_definitions.expression: SUM(counters_cell.pmSinrPuschDistr[0] * -5) + SUM(counters_cell.pmSinrPuschDistr[1] * -3.5) + SUM(counters_cell.pmSinrPuschDistr[2] * 0) + SUM(counters_cell.pmSinrPuschDistr[3] * 4) + SUM(counters_cell.pmSinrPuschDistr[4] * 8) + SUM(counters_cell.pmSinrPuschDistr[5] * 12) + SUM(counters_cell.pmSinrPuschDistr[6] * 15.5) + SUM(counters_cell.pmSinrPuschDistr[7] * 17) + SUM(counters_cell.pmSinrPuschDistr[8] * 20) FROM pm_stats://counters_cell

kpi_definitions.name: ul_pusch_sinr_hourly_denominator
kpi_definitions.expression: SUM(counters_cell.pmSinrPuschDistr[0]) + SUM(counters_cell.pmSinrPuschDistr[1]) + SUM(counters_cell.pmSinrPuschDistr[2]) + SUM(counters_cell.pmSinrPuschDistr[3]) + SUM(counters_cell.pmSinrPuschDistr[4]) + SUM(counters_cell.pmSinrPuschDistr[5]) + SUM(counters_cell.pmSinrPuschDistr[6]) + SUM(counters_cell.pmSinrPuschDistr[7]) + SUM(counters_cell.pmSinrPuschDistr[8]) FROM pm_stats://counters_cell

kpi_definitions.name: uplink_pusch_sinr_hourly_rss
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(ADD_INTEGER_TO_ARRAY_WITH_LIMIT(cell_guid.uplink_pusch_sinr_hourly_rss, kpi_cell_guid_60.ul_pusch_sinr_hourly, 8)) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60 LEFT JOIN kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60 as cell_guid ON kpi_cell_guid_60.guid = cell_guid.guid AND kpi_cell_guid_60.oss_id = cell_guid.oss_id AND kpi_cell_guid_60.fdn = cell_guid.fdn AND cell_guid.local_timestamp = (kpi_cell_guid_60.local_timestamp - interval 1 day) WHERE kpi_cell_guid_60.uplink_pusch_sinr_hourly_rss IS NULL
filter: kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60.utc_timestamp BETWEEN (date_trunc(''hour'', TO_TIMESTAMP(''${param.start_date_time}'')) - interval 1 day) and date_trunc(''hour'', TO_TIMESTAMP(''${param.end_date_time}''))

kpi_definitions.name: uplink_pusch_sinr_degradation
kpi_definitions.expression: FIRST(DEGRADATION_THRESHOLD(''MAX'', 0, kpi_cell_guid_60.uplink_pusch_sinr_hourly_rss, ''${param.ul_pusch_sinr_hourly_confidence_interval}'', ''${param.weekend_days}'', date_trunc(''day'', kpi_cell_guid_60.local_timestamp), 8, true)) FROM kpi_db://kpi_cell_guid_60 JOIN flm://cell_configuration_history ON cell_configuration_history.fdn = kpi_cell_guid_60.fdn AND cell_configuration_history.oss_id = kpi_cell_guid_60.oss_id
